    2    1/3/2015  287  Cases_Guinea  2769.0  [Cases, Guinea]  Cases  Guinea
    3    1/2/2015  286  Cases_Guinea     NaN  [Cases, Guinea]  Cases  Guinea
    4  12/31/2014  284  Cases_Guinea  2730.0  [Cases, Guinea]  Cases  Guinea

